/** * Created by Lenovo on 2019/8/10. */ import React from 'react'; import './personal.css'; import right from '../../images/personal/right.png'; import avatar from '../../images/personal/avatar.jpg'; import sale from '../../images/personal/sale.png'; import {Title} from '../../share'; import {getData, goNext} from '../../utils'; export default class Publish extends React.Component { constructor(props) { super(props); this.state = { account: '', password: '', } } goNextPage(){ goNext(this,'login'); } render() { return
<div className="cm-mlr-15"> <div className="cm-mtb-20 cm-flex cm-ai-c" onClick={()=>this.goNextPage()}> <img src={avatar} alt="" className="cm-img-50 cm-border-radius-half"/> <div className="cm-ml-10"> <div className="cm-fw-bold cm-fs-18">杏子</div> <div className="cm-c-999 cm-mt-10">当前卖出累计金额 <span className="cm-c-main cm-fs-18">￥12.78</span></div> </div> </div> <div className="cm-line"></div> <div className="cm-item cm-jc-sb"> <div> <img src="" alt=""/> <span className="cm-c-333">我发布的</span> </div> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"><span className="cm-c-999">0</span><img src={right} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/></div> </div> <div className="cm-item cm-jc-sb"> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"> <img src={sale} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/> <span className="cm-c-333 cm-ml-10">我卖出的</span> </div> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"><span className="cm-c-999">0</span><img src={right} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/></div> </div> <div className="cm-item cm-jc-sb"> <div> <img src="" alt=""/> <span className="cm-c-333">我买到的</span> </div> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"><span className="cm-c-999">0</span><img src={right} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/></div> </div> <div className="cm-item cm-jc-sb"> <div> <img src="" alt=""/> <span className="cm-c-333">修改密码</span> </div> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"><span className="cm-c-999">0</span><img src={right} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/></div> </div> <div className="cm-item cm-jc-sb"> <div> <img src="" alt=""/> <span className="cm-c-333">找回密码</span> </div> <div className="cm-flex cm-ai-c"><span className="cm-c-999">0</span><img src={right} alt="" className="cm-img-small-icon"/></div> </div> <div className="cm-tx-c cm-mt-40"><span className="cm-btn-small">安全退出</span></div> </div> </div> } }
